final_desc: - - Ester dari asam metakrilik :Asam monokarboksilat asiklik tidak jenuh, asam monokarboksilat siklik, anhidrida, halida, peroksida dan asam peroksinya; turunan halogenasi, sulfonasi, nitrasi atau nitrosasinya.;- - Esters of methacrylic acid :Unsaturated acyclic monocarboxylic acids, cyclic monocarboxylic acids, their anhydrides, halides, peroxides and peroxyacids; their halogenated, sulphonated, nitrated or nitrosated derivatives.

- - Lain-lain :Asam monokarboksilat asiklik tidak jenuh, asam monokarboksilat siklik, anhidrida, halida, peroksida dan asam peroksinya; turunan halogenasi, sulfonasi, nitrasi atau nitrosasinya.;- - Other :Unsaturated acyclic monocarboxylic acids, cyclic monocarboxylic acids, their anhydrides, halides, peroxides and peroxyacids; their halogenated, sulphonated, nitrated or nitrosated derivatives.
